ostatic behavior of simple structural schemes. Exact\nsolutions of Bishop rods are evaluated in terms of nonlocal parameter and\ncross-section gyration radius. Both hardening and softening structural\nresponses are predictable with a suitable tuning of the parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 10:55:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-21"}
