d\nCI models, these protocols successfully compute approximate majority with high\nprobability in the presence of leaks occurring at each step with probability\n$\\beta \\leq O\\left(\\sqrt{n \\log n}/n\\right)$, exhibiting a resilience to leaks\nsimilar to that of Byzantine agents in previous works.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 14:05:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 23:13:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 15:02:40 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 1 Apr 2023 17:10:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
